ZH: 我摔倒了，我的膝盖受伤了。
EN: I fell down and hurt my knee.

ZH: 运动时要保护好膝盖。
EN: Protect your knees when exercising.

ZH: 坐地铁的时候，常常要站着，时间长了膝盖会酸痛。
EN: When taking the subway, you often have to stand, which can make your knees ache after a while.

ZH: 她膝盖受伤了，需要静养几天。
EN: She hurt her knee and needs to rest for a few days.

ZH: 这种新款护膝能有效地保护膝盖免受外力伤害。
EN: This new knee pad design can effectively protect the knee from external impact.

ZH: 跳舞的时候，注意保护膝盖，避免扭伤。
EN: When dancing, take care of your knees to avoid spraining them.

ZH: 长时间久坐会对膝盖造成不良影响。
EN: Prolonged sitting can have adverse effects on the knees.

ZH: 我的膝盖关节发出奇怪的声音。
EN: My knee joints make strange noises.

ZH: 老年人常常出现膝盖疼痛的问题。
EN: Elderly people often suffer from knee pain.

ZH: 运动后，我会使用热敷来舒缓膝盖的不适。
EN: After exercising, I use a hot compress to relieve discomfort in my knees.

ZH: 他在比赛中严重扭伤了膝盖。
EN: He severely twisted his knee during the competition.

ZH: 孕妇要注意避免大幅度弯曲膝盖。
EN: Pregnant women should avoid bending their knees too much.

ZH: 我的膝盖骨折了，需要进行手术。
EN: I fractured my knee and need to undergo surgery.

ZH: 请坐下，不要让膝盖过度受力。
EN: Please sit down and don't put excessive force on your knees.

ZH: 他因为疲劳跑步而拉伤了膝盖。
EN: He strained his knee from running while fatigued.

ZH: 膝盖疼痛可能是关节炎的症状之一。
EN: Knee pain can be a symptom of arthritis.

ZH: 我每天晚上都会用冰敷敷在膝盖上，以舒缓肿痛。
EN: Every night I apply an ice pack to my knees to relieve swelling and pain.

ZH: 游泳是一种对膝盖较为轻松的运动方式。
EN: Swimming is a low-impact exercise for the knees.

ZH: 腿脚不自由的人需要使用助行器来减轻对膝盖的负担。
EN: People with limited mobility in their legs may need to use a walking aid to reduce strain on their knees.

ZH: 年轻人要注意保护膝盖，预防未来的关节问题。
EN: Young people should pay attention to knee protection to prevent future joint issues.
